<section id="concepts">
  <div class="section-tag">Core Concepts</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">6 Ideas That Unlock Everything</h2>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Master these fundamentals and you'll understand how every cloud service, architecture, and product fits together.</p>

  <div class="concepts-grid">

    <!-- 1 IaaS/PaaS/SaaS -->
    <div class="concept-card card-c1">
      <div class="concept-icon">🍕</div>
      <div class="concept-title">IaaS · PaaS · SaaS</div>
      <div class="concept-analogy">🍕 The Pizza Analogy</div>
      <div class="concept-desc">How much do you want to manage yourself? IaaS gives you raw ingredients (servers). PaaS gives you a kitchen (platform). SaaS delivers a finished pizza to your door (app). More abstraction = less control, less work.</div>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 300 130" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%">
        <!-- IaaS -->
        <rect x="5" y="8" width="85" height="114" rx="10" fill="rgba(244,114,182,0.1)" stroke="rgba(244,114,182,0.5)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <text x="47" y="26" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f472b6" font-size="10" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter">IaaS</text>
